{{version031}}
{{flavour|Exhales a stream of forgotten grief, leaving clouds of excruciating misery in its wake but skipping past creatures that would be vulnerable to it. These clouds of negative energy will rapidly drain the living of small fractions of their maximum health.}}

'''Mourning Wail''' is a monster-only spell that creates [[clouds]] of excruciating misery, which harm the player for 1/10th of their health every turn they remain inside it, and can be resisted with [[negative energy resistance]]. These clouds skip past susceptible allies.

{{monsters with spell}}

==History==
*Mourning Wail was added in [[0.31]].

